metadata.description: YASHA features modern anime art with a beautiful combination of JDM car culture, high level anime art, and deep lore, creating a unique and attractive art style. The collection is available in a 2:3 poster format, perfect for display, and also as a profile picture. Tangerine Labs is a pioneer in the anime space, with an experienced team to deliver exciting and unique utilities. Working with top tier Japanese studios, YASHA by Tangerine Labs is sure to become a sensation. Get in for the ride ...
metadata.name: YASHA by Tangerine Labs #1
